"""make sure production endpoint works as expected"""
all_news_df = news.company_news_rh(self.good_ticker)
assert isinstance(all_news_df, pd.DataFrame)
unique_values, unique_expected = helpers.find_uniques(list(all_news_df.
    columns.values), self.expected_news_cols)
assert unique_expected == []
if unique_values:
    pytest.xfail('Unexpected values from company_news_rh(): {}'.format(
        unique_values))
